<h1>International Weights and Measures Plugin For Rails</h1>

<p>
  This plugin allows you to use weight and measures in the same weight that one uses dates and times in rails.
</p>

Standard Syntax

n = 1.kg + 1.kg
puts n 
	=> "2.0 kg"

n += 1.mg
puts n.to_s(:long)
	 => "2.000001 kilograms"

n *= 4
puts n 
	=> "8.000004 kg"

n /= 2
puts n.to_s(:long)
	=> "4.000002 kilograms"

n -= 1.hg
puts n
	=> "-0.099995999998 kg"

